text: Wang Shuyuan (Chinese: 王淑媛, born August 1943) is a Chinese former long track speed skater, who was active in the 1960s. Shuyuan represented her nation four times at the World Allround Speed Skating Championships for Women. In 1963, finishing 6th overall, In 1964, finishing 13th overall, in 1965, finishing 12th overall and in 1966, finishing 11th overall. She also competed at other international competitions. She became national champion at the 1964 Chinese Allround Championships. == Records== === Personal records === ==References== Category:1943 births Category:Place of birth missing (living people) Category:Date of birth missing (living people) Category:Chinese female speed skaters Category:Living people
